        &lt;p&gt;Complete collection of JavaScript learning resources, frameworks, and development tools for modern web development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;JavaScript Fundamentals&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;javascript-fundamentals&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
